kuwait say opec 2.4 mln bpd below ceil kuwaiti oil minist sheikh ali al-khalifa al-sabah said opec wa produc well below it oil output ceil and thi would help price move higher , accord to a kuwaiti newspap interview . the al-rai al-aam newspap quot him as say opec wa pump 2.4 mln barrel per day ( bpd ) less than it 15.8 mln bpd ceil , while consum were draw down their petroleum stock at a rate of 4.5 mln bpd . as long as opec maintain it output curb , demand for it oil will rise in april and may , sheikh ali said , ad that kuwait wa strongli commit to it opec quota .